abstract: Secretary of State Clinton makes the rounds on the Sunday shows to talk about Libya and Iraq.
snippet: Secretary of State Clinton makes the rounds on the Sunday shows to talk about Libya and Iraq.
lead_paragraph: With the death of Col. Muammar el-Qaddafi in Libya on Thursday and President Obama's announcement on Friday that all United States troops would be out of Iraq by the end of the year, many are wondering what these developments will mean for American interests.
